          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is wifi on all over the campus which students can access.",
          "name": "Review Rebel",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "For extra co -curriculum activities all facilities are available.",
          "name": "Pratik Shalikrao Gorade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Most advance tools and technology currently available in campus.",
          "name": "Pratik Shalikrao Gorade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "For sports every thing is available in college and ground and stadium also available.",
          "name": "Pratik Shalikrao Gorade",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has a library and all the water facilities.",
          "name": "Shubham Aghav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "College also supports students to develop as much number of projects as possible. Teachers help us to develop them and guide us with the problema faced during the development of that project.",
          "name": "Basavraj Sirasgaonkar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college campus have greenery everywhere and neat and clean campus makes the surrounding beautiful and clean.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Updated technical labs with good network.",
          "name": "Samreen Yunus Chaudhari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are many groups like GDSC , IITB group .",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "No financial aid or scholarship is provided",
