          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "No purified drinking water is available on the college building for students",
          "name": "Review Rebel",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Not proper computer labs are available for CSE students.",
